<section xml:id="quiz-8">

    <title>Week 8 Quiz</title>
    
    <p>
        Suppose that <m>f:[0,\iy) \to \bR</m> is continuous and satisfies
        <md>
            <mrow>\int_0^1 f(xt) \dt = 0, \qquad \forall x >0.</mrow>
        </md>
        Prove that <m>f(x) \equiv 0</m>.
    </p>

</section>